	   <tr><td colspan=2>Keep in mind that if you want to make the bow after you do the quest, you will need (2) Dwarven wires, and (2) Micro servos for each try.  The original bag takes a spiderLING web, treant wood, dwarven wire, and a microservo...but to make the bow you need yet another micro servo, yet another dwarven wire, along with the plane and the treant stave given by Maesyn.  Oh, and BTW at skill 102 I've only been able to do it ONCE and I've gone through DOZENS and DOZENS of parts.  All I got for my trouble was the XP for gathering parts and 2 points in fletch.  (And killed once on Sister's Island...THAT was fun.)<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
